# Validate Email Addresses

This specification verifies email address validation.

## Scenario: Validate valid email addresses
    * Verify that "example@example.com" is a valid email address
    * Verify that "john.doe@example.co.uk" is a valid email address

## Scenario: Validate invalid email addresses
    * Verify that "invalid_email.com" is not a valid email address
    * Verify that "john@doe" is not a valid email address
